{"tid":2451730,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果中國呢一百年行蔡元培1912年提出嘅教育制度","createTime":"2021-03-18T10:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T13:26:00.000Z","uid":280898,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66323310d08ab81b776bcea6dc8b49e91749144f","tid":2451730,"uid":280898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"蔡元培作為民國第一任教育總長，發表咗「對於教育方針之意見一文」，文中提出五項<span class=\"red\">基礎</span>教育：<br />\n<br />\n軍國民教育：軍事訓練加國民國族意識培養<br />\n<br />\n實利教育：生活、職業技能教育<br />\n<br />\n公民道德教育：教人點做公民、講法治、人權、民主等概念<br />\n<br />\n世界觀教育：學做世界公民，了解其他國家文化、技術<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">美感教育</span>：教人點欣賞藝術音樂文化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一百年後嘅今日睇返都仲係好前衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中世界觀、公民道德、軍國民教育都係教當時革命後由帝國人民轉化到世界公民、建立新嘅國民意識<br />\n<br />\n加上喺中國人社會講美感教育今日睇返真係好有突破性<br />\n<br />\n如果呢一百年中國真係行到呢套基礎教育，國民質素隨時拍得住日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果上面有理解錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f8de008cbaf51d284597c1ba28e1c42fa355ef","tid":2451730,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"比人暗殺嗰個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed940187b9a1b313bf2f2a2eaad6773fadd6432","tid":2451730,"uid":280898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09f8de008cbaf51d284597c1ba28e1c42fa355ef","tid":2451730,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"比人暗殺嗰個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"唔係，佢喺好似係病死嘅，仲要喺香港過身"},{"pid":"2d5c369c60e99fee49e0f402200152163e689a4f","tid":2451730,"uid":280898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03